{"type":"info-page","slug":"jmm/cgi/alerts/etoc","journal":"jmm","canonical":"https://www.sgmjournals.org/jmm/cgi/alerts/etoc","title":"Journal of Medical Microbiology","bodyHtml":"<div id=\"hw-login-msg-box\">\n        <div id=\"hw-login-msg-box-text\">\n          <div>\n            <span><strong>Sign In</strong> with your email address to use this service.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div id=\"hw-login-item-group\">\n        <div id=\"hw-login-etoc-item-group\">\n          <div id=\"hw-login-etoc-item-header\">\n            eTOCs - <em>\"electronic Table of Contents\"</em>\n          </div>\n          <div id=\"hw-login-etoc-item-subheader\">\n            Subscribe, Unsubscribe, or Edit your eTOCs Settings\n          </div>\n          <div id=\"hw-login-etoc-item-description\">\n            eTOCs is a free service providing table of contents or a notification of availability when new issues of Journal of Medical Microbiology are published online.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div id=\"hw-login-email-only-sign-in-group\">\n        <div id=\"hw-login-email-only-sign-in-header\" class=\"hw-login-section-header\">\n          <img alt=\"*\" width=\"9\" height=\"15\" src=\"/shared/img/pages/login/redtri.gif\">Sign In to <span>eTOCs</span> with your Email Address\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"hw-login-email-only-sign-in-box\">\n          <form action=\"/cgi/alerts/etoc\" method=\"post\" class=\"hw-ac-standalone-form hw-login-form\">\n            <fieldset>\n              <input value=\"http://jmm.sgmjournals.org/content/62/Pt_4/499.abstract\" type=\"hidden\" name=\"login_referer\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"email-only-login\" value=\"true\"><legend class=\"ext-legend\">Sign In with your Email Address</legend> <span><label for=\"email\">Email</label> <input type=\"text\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" value=\"\" size=\"30\" maxlength=\"100\" tabindex=\"4\"></span> <span class=\"login-submit\"><input type=\"submit\" name=\"signin\" value=\"Sign In\" tabindex=\"5\"></span>\n            </fieldset>\n          </form>\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"hw-login-email-only-sign-in-text-below\" class=\"hw-login-section-body\">\n          Once you have signed in with your email address you can:\n          <ul class=\"hw-login-option-list\">\n            <li>select/modify your eTOCs</li>\n            <li>follow the \"Unsubscribe\" link to stop your eTOCs</li>\n            <li>to change your Email Address: Delete your old eTOCs by signing in with your old email address and then following the \"Unsubscribe\" link. Then sign in with your new email address to select your eTOCs.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>"}